@startuml sequence_update_recruiter
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Update a Recruiter Record

actor Candidate
participant "Markdown Editor" as Editor
participant "recruiter-vendor-list.md" as RecruiterList
participant "job-search Skill" as Skill

Candidate -> Editor : Open docs/recruiter-vendor-list.md
Editor -> RecruiterList : Read current table
RecruiterList --> Editor : Return all recruiter rows

Candidate -> Editor : Locate recruiter row;\nupdate Last Contacted Date,\nEngagement Status, Notes
Editor -> RecruiterList : Write updated file
RecruiterList --> Editor : Save confirmed
Editor --> Candidate : File saved

note over Candidate : No automated write-back.\nSkill reads updated data on next run.

Candidate -> Skill : Run job-search (next cycle)
Skill -> RecruiterList : Read updated recruiter list
RecruiterList --> Skill : Return all records
Skill -> Skill : Recompute days since contact\nfor all High-priority records
Skill --> Candidate : Report updated follow-up status

@enduml
